{
  "stem": "4032.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And just before the war, a year, my younger brother got married and moved out of the city to the city where he married-- married the girl.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I became more active in the business, started to.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Any other--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My parents name was-- my father's name was Natan.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My mother's name was Touga.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my sister's name was Rivka and Hella.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As far as I know, yeah.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All the time in that town.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Approximately 500 Jewish families.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Total, I wouldn't exactly know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I would say two-thirds more of Polish people than-- than Jewish.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, in-- in-- before the war, it wasn't too bad.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But when the war started, they got carried away by the Germans, and they're trying to help the Germans as much as they could to show who is a Jew and who is not a Jew.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] not too big of a help to the Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Of course, they couldn't do much, but if there was something to be done, it wasn't done anyhow.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we had small incidents, like the guy that rented the-- the-- the place where we were organized, the Betar, when he got drunk, [LAUGHS] he said he's going to kill all the Jews there and that-- and he was the landlord of our-- but when he got sober, he calmed down and he apologized for what he did.",
      "word_count": 59
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and-- and that was the life.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, that was the thing that happened.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] In 1939, of course, when the war broke out, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the Germans came in approximately about 10 days after the war broke out.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, in the relations to-- the town is called Przedecz.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it's the [POLISH] in [POLISH].",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
